snippet.title: Paint the Town Red VR - Official Announcent Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Paint the Town Red VR is a virtual reality version of the popular first-person melee brawler. Coming to Meta Quest, PSVR 2, and Steam VR in early 2024, you'll be able to shoot, slab, smash, and slash your way through hordes of blocky enemies.
